8
00:00:47.180 --> 00:00:49.693
<i>I spent most of my time
underwater...</i>

9
00:00:49.776 --> 00:00:52.513
<i>finding things that had
been lost for centuries.</i>

10
00:00:54.088 --> 00:00:55.468
<i>My work was solitary.</i>

11
00:00:55.551 --> 00:00:58.453
<i>researching and then
setting out on my missions.</i>

12
00:00:59.291 --> 00:01:01.243
<i>But I liked it that way.</i>

13
00:01:01.326 --> 00:01:04.426
<i>I controlled my own destiny
with no one to report to.</i>

14
00:01:05.099 --> 00:01:06.461
<i>But all that changed...</i>

15
00:01:07.464 --> 00:01:09.233
<i>when the solar flare hit.</i>

16
00:01:11.468 --> 00:01:14.586
<i>The world was thrown
into darkness and chaos.</i>

17
00:01:14.669 --> 00:01:15.518
