1033
01:05:09.302 --> 01:05:12.941
<i>Repeat. We can have a team
at Simserhof by 1400 hours.</i>

1034
01:05:14.505 --> 01:05:17.275
Copy. Moulin 2. Moulin 1. out.

1035
01:05:18.377 --> 01:05:19.508
