1043
01:06:33.320 --> 01:06:34.583
Hmm.

1044
01:06:43.264 --> 01:06:44.494
Volkov. look.

1045
01:06:49.237 --> 01:06:52.667
VOLKOV: Forty-eight. 58...

1046
01:06:55.738 --> 01:06:58.607
We're going to
the Nancy Air Force Base.

1047
01:06:59.742 --> 01:07:01.577
(BLOWS AIR)

1048
01:07:04.054 --> 01:07:05.614
No. we're not.

1049
01:07:08.520 --> 01:07:11.341
We're going to Simserhof.

1050
01:07:11.424 --> 01:07:15.345
And we're gonna meet
a very special lady.

1051
01:07:15.428 --> 01:07:17.545
Tell the conductor we're taking
the route to the bridge.

1052
01:07:17.628 --> 01:07:18.726
Understood.

1053
01:07:20.136 --> 01:07:21.989
Well. I think
he wants his reward.

1054
01:07:22.072 --> 01:07:23.518
-One thousand bullets.
-(WRAITH COUGHS)

1055
01:07:23.601 --> 01:07:25.685
VOLKOV: How many
do you think he deserves?

1056
01:07:25.768 --> 01:07:27.702
-Three.
-Agreed.

1057
01:07:31.774 --> 01:07:34.049
(DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYING)

1058
01:08:27.764 --> 01:08:29.797
(ENGINE REVVING)

1059
01:08:55.462 --> 01:08:57.645
(SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING)

1060
