1064
01:09:16.778 --> 01:09:19.799
No keypad. no interface.
no biometric scanners.

1065
01:09:19.882 --> 01:09:21.387
No handle.

1066
01:09:22.720 --> 01:09:24.489
There's a camera there.

1067
01:09:25.327 --> 01:09:26.656
And there.

1068
01:09:28.330 --> 01:09:30.330
They had to power up
this place somehow.

1069
01:09:33.896 --> 01:09:35.203
Look.

1070
01:09:37.438 --> 01:09:38.899
(DOOR THUDS)

1071
01:09:49.681 --> 01:09:51.846
(SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES)

1072
01:09:56.325 --> 01:09:58.358
(GENERATOR WHIRRING)

1073
01:10:00.692 --> 01:10:02.560
Something's still running.

1074
01:10:03.299 --> 01:10:04.661
DREA: Yeah.

1075
01:10:05.862 --> 01:10:07.847
