1076
01:10:07.930 --> 01:10:09.567
Maybe not. (SIGHS)

1077
01:10:10.801 --> 01:10:12.537
(TORCH CLICKS)

1078
01:10:16.708 --> 01:10:18.906
(GENERATOR POWERS UP)

1079
01:10:22.450 --> 01:10:24.171
