for the vault.

1089
01:10:56.385 --> 01:10:58.337
JAKE: Right.
Yeah. that's our way in.

1090
01:10:58.420 --> 01:11:01.571
MAN: (OVER RADIO) <i>Moulin 1.</i>
<i>Volkov's heading to you.</i>

1091
01:11:01.654 --> 01:11:04.919
<i>Fifty miles out.
I repeat. 50 miles out.</i>

1092
01:11:05.526 --> 01:11:06.774
Moulin 1. Copy.

1093
01:11:06.857 --> 01:11:07.907
They're close.

1094
01:11:07.990 --> 01:11:09.315
Yeah.
these stairs should take me

1095
01:11:09.398 --> 01:11:10.214
