1096
01:11:10.297 --> 01:11:12.912
If I can get in here.
down this shaft

1097
01:11:12.995 --> 01:11:14.782
and along this air duct.

1098
01:11:14.865 --> 01:11:17.767
then that should take me
right into the vault.

1099
01:11:18.770 --> 01:11:20.458
DREA: Okay.

1100
01:11:20.541 --> 01:11:23.428
JAKE: If this fan's operational.
we're gonna have to kill it.

1101
01:11:23.511 --> 01:11:24.873
And then what?

1102
01:11:26.547 --> 01:11:28.778
I'll figure it out.
Let's get to it.

1103
01:11:33.983 --> 01:11:36.606
Hey. remember
that service road we saw?

1104
01:11:36.689 --> 01:11:38.887
I bet that leads
to the solar panels.

1105
01:11:39.956 --> 01:11:41.248
I'll take them out.

1106
01:11:41.331 --> 01:11:42.990
All right. let's get to work.

1107
01:11:43.795 --> 01:11:45.795
(THRILLING MUSIC PLAYING)

1108
01:12:20.733 --> 01:12:22.337
(ENGINE REVS)

1109
